---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Building2, Zap, LayoutTemplate, ArrowRight } from 'lucide-react';
---

<Layout title="thEnvites - Digital invitations, engineered to elevate.">
  <div class="flex flex-col">
    {/* Hero Section */}
    <section class="px-5 md:px-margin-desktop py-24 md:py-32 max-w-360 mx-auto w-full grid grid-cols-12">
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-10">
        <h1 class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-[80px] font-bold leading-[1.1] mb-8 tracking-[-0.04em]">
          Digital invitations, <br />
          <span class="text-on-surface-variant">engineered to elevate.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="font-body text-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mb-12">
          Stop sending generic links. Deploy beautiful, premium invitation templates for weddings, milestone parties, and elite mixers with the invites platform built for modern hosts.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a
            href="/templates"
            class="bg-on-background text-background px-8 py-4 font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-background hover:text-on-background border border-on-background transition-all duration-300"
          >
            Create an Envite
          </a>
          <a
            href="/templates"
            class="bg-transparent text-on-background px-8 py-4 font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-on-background hover:text-background border border-on-background transition-all duration-300"
          >
            View Core Templates
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Editorial SEO Section */}
    <section class="px-5 md:px-margin-desktop py-32 md:py-section-gap border-t border-border-surgical bg-background">
      <div class="max-w-360 mx-auto w-full">
        <div class="mb-16 md:mb-24 flex items-center gap-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-on-surface flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="font-serif italic text-lg leading-none mt-1">i</span>
          </div>
          <span class="font-mono text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-on-surface">
            Editorial / Platform Architecture
          </span>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-y-16 lg:gap-x-6 xl:gap-x-12 lg:gap-y-0">
          {/* Left Column */}
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 relative">
            <div class="sticky top-12">
              <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-8">
                Modern Event Planning Starts with the Perfect Digital Invitation.
              </h2>
              <div class="w-full h-px bg-border-surgical mb-8"></div>
              <p class="font-body text-base lg:text-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed max-w-sm">
                The landscape of event hosting has fundamentally shifted. Whether you are coordinating an intimate weekend gathering or a grand scale celebration, the invitation you send is the absolute first point of contact your guests will have with your event. It sets the tone, dictates the aesthetic expectation, and streamlines the logistical flow of the entire day. At thEnvites, we engineered a fast, fluid, and completely free invitation maker designed to replace uninspiring group texts and cluttered paper cards with sleek, high-performance digital event hubs.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          {/* Right Column */}
          <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-16 md:space-y-24 lg:border-l border-border-surgical lg:pl-16 xl:pl-24">
            
            <article>
              <div class="mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
                <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-accent-energy uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">01 &mdash; Scale</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Explore Curated Invitation Templates for Every Scale</h3>
              <div class="space-y-6">
                <p class="first-letter:text-6xl first-letter:font-headline first-letter:float-left first-letter:pr-4 first-letter:leading-[0.8] first-letter:text-on-surface font-body text-base text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
                  Great events shouldn't be gated behind complex graphic design software or expensive specialized agencies. Our intuitive platform acts as a centralized invitation maker that places premium design directly into your hands. We deliberately avoid overwhelming you with infinite, poorly formatted options. Instead, our design framework provides highly optimized, hyper-focused invitation templates built on strict grid systems and beautiful typography layouts.
                </p>
                <p class="font-body text-base text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
                  For hosts celebrating life's most meaningful milestones, our dedicated wedding invitation engine pairs luxury editorial styling with seamless functional utility. We understand that a wedding invitation needs to evoke a deep sense of elegance, which is why our curated wedding invitation templates focus heavily on sweeping minimalist layouts, clean content spacing, and clear interactive scheduling.
                </p>
                <p class="font-body text-base text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
                  Planning a different type of celebration? Our platform adapts instantly. From high-energy weekend get-togethers requiring a sharp birthday invitation layout to corporate product reveals demanding minimalist structure, our suite covers the entire spectrum of modern hosting. Every single layout inside this free invitation maker comes completely integrated with fast media loading zones, letting you drop in up to three stunning images to personalize your space without cluttering the structural interface.
                </p>
              </div>
            </article>

            <div class="w-full h-px bg-border-surgical"></div>

            <article>
              <div class="mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
                <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-accent-energy uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">02 &mdash; Utility</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl font-bold mb-6">The Functional Power Behind The Invites</h3>
              <div class="space-y-6">
                <p class="font-body text-base text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
                  <span class="font-bold text-on-surface">A modern web-based invitation should do far more than just look beautiful on a screen;</span> it needs to operate like an intuitive application. When you construct an event space through the invites engine, your page is deployed as a highly responsive web interface built to function flawlessly across desktop browsers and mobile screens alike.
                </p>
                <p class="font-body text-base text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
                  Your guests receive an elegant, custom-tailored URL that details exactly what they need to know: when to arrive, where to go, and how to prepare. By utilizing a web-first distribution method, updates to your event itinerary, venue location adjustments, or timing changes map instantly to your live link. No more frantic follow-up messages or confusing clarification strings.
                </p>
              </div>
            </article>

            <div class="w-full h-px bg-border-surgical"></div>

            <article>
              <div class="mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
                <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-accent-energy uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">03 &mdash; Bespoke</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Tailor-Made Designs for Distinct Events</h3>
              <div class="space-y-6">
                <p class="font-body text-base text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
                  While our core system empowers users to rapidly configure pre-built components into striking digital cards, we recognize that highly unique events sometimes demand an entirely custom architectural touch. If your celebration scales beyond our primary template options, our professional in-house studio is ready to collaborate. By visiting our dedicated Contact page, you can submit your detailed parameters directly to our technical team, allowing us to map out, design, and deploy an exclusive, fully bespoke event layout built explicitly around your personal vision.
                </p>
                <a href="/contact" class="block mt-8">
                  <div class="p-8 border border-border-surgical bg-surface-container relative group cursor-pointer transition-colors hover:border-on-surface">
                    <div class="absolute right-8 top-8 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
                      <ArrowRight className="w-5 h-5 text-on-surface" />
                    </div>
                    <p class="font-headline text-xl text-on-surface leading-relaxed max-w-sm">
                      Ditch the complex design portals, avoid the printing costs, and give your guests an elite digital experience from the very first click. <span class="font-italic opacity-70">Publish your next event hub with absolute precision.</span>
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </a>
              </div>
            </article>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Custom Pipeline Callout */}
    <section class="px-5 md:px-margin-desktop py-24 md:py-section-gap bg-surface-black border-y border-border-surgical text-background">
      <div class="max-w-360 mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl tracking-tight mb-8 text-background font-bold">
          Looking for absolute architectural freedom?
        </h2>
        <p class="font-body text-lg text-background/70 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-12">
          If your milestone event requires a completely bespoke, tailored digital footprint that goes beyond standard presets, our design collective can build it for you from scratch.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-block border border-background text-background px-12 py-5 font-mono text-xs font-bold hover:bg-background hover:text-surface-black transition-all duration-300 uppercase tracking-widest"
        >
          Contact Our Studio for a Custom Build &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
